sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Frontend
    participant API as Symfony API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    User->>Frontend: Select a locked channel
    Frontend->>API: GET /api/channels/{id}/messages
    API->>API: Validate JWT
    API->>DB: Load channel and memberships
    DB-->>API: Channel access data

    alt User is not a channel member
        API-->>Frontend: 403 Forbidden
        Frontend->>Frontend: Set locked state
        Frontend-->>User: Show locked channel message
        Frontend-->>User: Disable message composer
    else User is a channel member
        API->>DB: Load messages
        DB-->>API: Message list
        API-->>Frontend: 200 OK + messages
        Frontend-->>User: Display discussion
    end
